description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. This is round 1 of 4 of the live November match up between Team Ice and The Goddesses.

The Goddesses are mathematically eliminated from the playoffs. Now they are fighting for respect and pride after suffering the hardest loss of any team. Losing Isis Love as team Captain is not an easy thing to overcome in such a competitive league. Wenona did a great job stepping in but the fire was lost..

Team Ice also had to replace a wrestler this season with the injury to Mellanie Monroe. Holly Stevens stepped in and the team is as strong as ever. However, they need to learn to work as a team.

The first round was brutal. Holly asserted herself early as a [REDACTED] to reckon with. Amazing one on one action and great double teams. At the end of 12 minutes Team Ice takes the lead going into the locker room.
title: 4 compete in the only Tag Team non-scripted wresting in the world Brutal holds & submissions!
